</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='634' id='t-634'>Let's talk about manias.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='4691' id='t-4691'>Let's start with Beatlemania.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 0:17
