<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 0:19
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='8873' id='t-8873'>Hysterical teenagers,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='11000' id='t-11000'>crying, screaming, pandemonium.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
