<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 0:28
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='17488' id='t-17488'>Sports mania:</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='19000' id='t-19000'>deafening crowds,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='22000' id='t-22000'>all for one idea --
get the ball in the net.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='26295' id='t-26295'>(Recording) Goal!</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='28000' id='t-28000'>Okay, religious mania:</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='30000' id='t-30000'>there's rapture, there's weeping,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='33000' id='t-33000'>there's visions.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='35000' id='t-35000'>Manias can be good.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='37008' id='t-37008'>Manias can be alarming.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='40106' id='t-40106'>Or manias can be deadly.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 0:53
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='42315' id='t-42315'>(Recording of crowd cheering)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 0:57
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='46000' id='t-46000'>The world has a new mania.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='48000' id='t-48000'>A mania for learning English.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='50632' id='t-50632'>Listen as Chinese students
practice their English,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='54174' id='t-54174'>by screaming it:</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 1:07
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='56000' id='t-56000'>Teacher: ... change my life!</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
