<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='83000' id='t-83000'>How many people
are trying to learn English worldwide?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='86167' id='t-86167'>Two billion of them.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 1:39
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='88690' id='t-88690'>Students: A t-shirt. A dress.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 1:43
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='92827' id='t-92827'>Jay Walker: In Latin America,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='94470' id='t-94470'>in India,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='96144' id='t-96144'>in Southeast Asia,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='97795' id='t-97795'>and most of all, in China.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='100571' id='t-100571'>If you're a Chinese student,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='102000' id='t-102000'>you start learning English
in the third grade, by law.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='107444' id='t-107444'>That's why this year,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='109214' id='t-109214'>China will become the world's largest
English-speaking country.</span>
</span>
</p>
