<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 2:07
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='116230' id='t-116230'>Why English?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='117572' id='t-117572'>In a single word: opportunity.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='119761' id='t-119761'>Opportunity for a better life, a job,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='122587' id='t-122587'>to be able to pay for school,
or put better food on the table.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='126000' id='t-126000'>Imagine a student taking
a giant test for three full days.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='130563' id='t-130563'>Her score on this one test
literally determines her future.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='135040' id='t-135040'>She studies 12 hours a day</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='137548' id='t-137548'>for three years to prepare.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='140312' id='t-140312'>Twenty-five percent of her grade
is based on English.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='145264' id='t-145264'>It's called the gaokao, and 80 million
high school Chinese students</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='149979' id='t-149979'>have already taken this grueling test.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='152375' id='t-152375'>The intensity to learn English</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='154668' id='t-154668'>is almost unimaginable,
