<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='187333' id='t-187333'>Not likely.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='188579' id='t-188579'>English is the world's second language.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='191500' id='t-191500'>Your native language is your life.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='193595' id='t-193595'>But with English you can become
