<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='207000' id='t-207000'>The world has other universal languages.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='210499' id='t-210499'>Mathematics is the language of science.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='213555' id='t-213555'>Music is the language of emotions.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='216571' id='t-216571'>And now English is becoming
